<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/72390675-huck-flynn"><img alt="" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_100x100-259587f1619f5253426a4fa6fb508831.png" /></a>
