<span id="freeTextContainer16196016446781741044">Auster&apos;s trilogy of stories are basically the same story with a different slant. Written in the guise of a detective story : man seeks man but is really seeking himself and the nature of his being? All very metaphysical/existential if you like that sort of thing, but highly readable.</span>
  <span id="freeText16196016446781741044" style="display:none">Auster's trilogy of stories are basically the same story with a different slant. Written in the guise of a detective story : man seeks man but is really seeking himself and the nature of his being? All very metaphysical/existential if you like that sort of thing, but highly readable.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16196016446781741044" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

